      <p id="u1413-2">You want the best possible protection for whomever – or whatever – you truly love. We’re in business to help you understand and protect yourself from risk. Find out how we can help you to manage the risks you face, making your life more secure and enable you to live a happier life.</p>
      <p id="u1413-3">&nbsp;</p>
      <p id="u1413-5">We understand being in the diaspora has its own challenges and we have built insurance products to give you peace while you are away</p>
     </div>
     <ul class="AccordionWidget clearfix colelem" id="accordionu1416"><!-- vertical box -->
      <li class="AccordionPanel clearfix colelem" id="u1417"><!-- vertical box --><div class="AccordionPanelTab clearfix colelem" id="u1418-5"><!-- content --><div id="u1418-4"><p><span id="u1418" class="shared_content" data-content-guid="u1418_content">​</span><span class="actAsInlineDiv normal_text" id="u1806"><!-- content --><span class="actAsDiv clip_frame excludeFromNormalFlow" id="u1798"><!-- image --><img class="temp_no_img_src" id="u1798_img" data-orig-src="images/motor-crop-u1798.png?crc=4261567028" alt="" width="853" height="92" src="images/blank.gif?crc=4208392903"/></span></span><span class="shared_content" data-content-guid="u1418-4_0_2_content"></span></p></div></div><div class="AccordionPanelContent disn clearfix colelem" id="u1419"><!-- group --><div class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" id="u1420-5" data-content-guid="u1420-5_content"><!-- content --><p id="u1420-3">If your car were stolen or damaged in an accident would you be able to afford to replace it? Your vehicle is an asset that needs protecting. Motor insurance is essential because it covers damages to your car as well as damages or injuries to other drivers, their vehicles or pedestrians. Zimnat General Insurance offers a range of motor insurance options to suit your budget and needs <span id="u1420-2">[LEARN MORE]</span></p></div></div></li>
      <li class="AccordionPanel clearfix colelem" id="u1421"><!-- vertical box --><div class="AccordionPanelTab clearfix colelem" id="u1424-5"><!-- content --><div id="u1424-4"><p><span id="u1424" class="shared_content" data-content-guid="u1424_content">​</span><span class="actAsInlineDiv normal_text" id="u1816"><!-- content --><span class="actAsDiv clip_frame excludeFromNormalFlow" id="u1811"><!-- image --><img class="temp_no_img_src" id="u1811_img" data-orig-src="images/home-crop-u1811.png?crc=443392694" alt="" width="854" height="90" src="images/blank.gif?crc=4208392903"/></span></span><span class="shared_content" data-content-guid="u1424-4_0_2_content"></span></p></div></div><div class="AccordionPanelContent disn clearfix colelem" id="u1422"><!-- group --><div class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" id="u1866-5" data-content-guid="u1866-5_content"><!-- content --><p id="u1866-3">For the protection of your home, household contents and valuable personal property. Our Domestic Insurance covers against loss or damage to your household contents (Household cover), and loss or damage to the residential building itself (Homeowner cover). The two policies can be combined to provide you with our ‘All-in-one’ Domestic cover. Additionally, we offer cover for specified valuables such as jewellery, clothing, laptops etc. that can be carried on your person for use outdoors. <span id="u1866-2">[LEARN MORE]</span></p></div></div></li>
      <li class="AccordionPanel clearfix colelem" id="u1425"><!-- vertical box --><div class="AccordionPanelTab clearfix colelem" id="u1428-5"><!-- content --><div id="u1428-4"><p><span id="u1428" class="shared_content" data-content-guid="u1428_content">​</span><span class="actAsInlineDiv normal_text" id="u1826"><!-- content --><span class="actAsDiv clip_frame excludeFromNormalFlow" id="u1821"><!-- image --><img class="temp_no_img_src" id="u1821_img" data-orig-src="images/travel-crop-u1821.png?crc=4180987299" alt="" width="854" height="93" src="images/blank.gif?crc=4208392903"/></span></span><span class="shared_content" data-content-guid="u1428-4_0_2_content"></span></p></div></div><div class="AccordionPanelContent disn clearfix colelem" id="u1426"><!-- group --><div class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" id="u1872-5" data-content-guid="u1872-5_content"><!-- content --><p id="u1872-3">Travel insurance is often one of the small things that we forget to arrange. Our Travel policy offers you one of the most comprehensive range of world class travel insurance available. You can enjoy your holiday without any worries with our travel insurance. We cover medical expenses incurred when overseas, cancellation costs of both flights and accommodation, personal injury, lost baggage and more. <span id="u1872-2">[LEARN MORE]</span></p></div></div></li>
      <li class="AccordionPanel clearfix colelem" id="u1455"><!-- vertical box --><div class="AccordionPanelTab clearfix colelem" id="u1458-5"><!-- content --><div id="u1458-4"><p><span id="u1458" class="shared_content" data-content-guid="u1458_content">​</span><span class="actAsInlineDiv normal_text" id="u1836"><!-- content --><span class="actAsDiv clip_frame excludeFromNormalFlow" id="u1831"><!-- image --><img class="temp_no_img_src" id="u1831_img" data-orig-src="images/medical-crop-u1831.png?crc=35510441" alt="" width="853" height="89" src="images/blank.gif?crc=4208392903"/></span></span><span class="shared_content" data-content-guid="u1458-4_0_2_content"></span></p></div></div><div class="AccordionPanelContent disn clearfix colelem" id="u1456"><!-- group --><div class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" id="u1875-7" data-content-guid="u1875-7_content"><!-- content --><p id="u1875-2">While there's no way to prevent all accidents from happening, we can take steps to protect you, financially, from the inconvenience they can cause. Personal accident insurance can pay a lump sum benefit if you suffer one of the listed injuries – helping you cope financially while you recover. We also offer a Hospital Cash plan which gives you the benefit of cash for every day that you or your loved ones are hospitalised.</p><p id="u1875-5">&nbsp;<span id="u1875-4">[LEARN MORE]</span></p></div></div></li>
      <li class="AccordionPanel clearfix colelem" id="u1471"><!-- vertical box --><div class="AccordionPanelTab clearfix colelem" id="u1473-5"><!-- content --><div id="u1473-4"><p><span id="u1473" class="shared_content" data-content-guid="u1473_content">​</span><span class="actAsInlineDiv normal_text" id="u1846"><!-- content --><span class="actAsDiv clip_frame excludeFromNormalFlow" id="u1841"><!-- image --><img class="temp_no_img_src" id="u1841_img" data-orig-src="images/funeral-crop-u1841.png?crc=4262928775" alt="" width="854" height="86" src="images/blank.gif?crc=4208392903"/></span></span><span class="shared_content" data-content-guid="u1473-4_0_2_content"></span></p></div></div><div class="AccordionPanelContent disn clearfix colelem" id="u1472"><!-- group --><div class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" id="u1878-7" data-content-guid="u1878-7_content"><!-- content --><p id="u1878-2">Many Zimbabweans abroad underestimate the burden the put their families on when they pass away in an untimely manner. We at Zimnat understand that protecting your family and friends from the burden of your funeral and/or body repatriation expenses is very important. Guarantee yourself a dignified funeral and allow your family and friends a chance to celebrate your life instead of begging for help.</p><p id="u1878-5">&nbsp;<span id="u1878-4">[LEARN MORE]</span></p></div></div></li>
